  & D: Mode B           & --- & 198{,}1 & 59{,}5\,\% \\
\addlinespace
\multirow{3}{*}{$+25$\,dB (gần)}
  & B: SVD (tham chiếu) & --- & 332{,}7 & tham chiếu \\
